(thirdQuint)The Effect of Anesthesia Type on Pulmonary Function.

 Sixty elder patients will be randomly assigned to General anesthesia or Neuraxial anesthesia groups.

 Spirometry, will be performed at pre-operative and post-operative terms.

 Pulmonary function tests will be evaluated.

